srppp_pests.Rd

Table of pesticide targets ("pests") extracted from all years starting 2011

Usage

srppp_pests

Format

tibble A table of all pesticide target names in German, French and Italian, a scientific name if available and the columns 'earliest' and 'latest', indicating the earliest and latest year of occurrence.
